title: Karl.Start
tags:
---
<<showcharactername Managers Karl>>
<<if not isvisited("Karl", "Start")>>
    Welcome, friend, to Mayfair!
    Its not as much of a special place as Grandrun, but we manage.
    Have you passed through Neverre or Borealis on your way here?
    [[Karl.Ask]]
<<else>>
    [[Karl.Idle]]
<<endif>>
===

title: Karl.Ask
tags: 
---
<<displaypromptmenu Managers LocAAA>>
Where are you from, my friend?
<<set $direction to react("position")>>
<<set $origin to react("city", "placeOfOrigin")>>
<<if $direction eq "West">>
    Oh, really? I guess that means I don't need to show you the town.
    [[Karl.ChildOfLadyKatherine]]
<<elseif $direction eq "East">>
    Oh, you're from the east? I hear there is a big conflict going on there, right?
    [[Karl.Explain]]
<<elseif $direction eq "North">>
    That's far up in the north, isnt it? Is it cold up there?
    [[Karl.Explain]]
<<elseif $direction eq "South">>
    Ah, a sunny town in the south, how lovely.
    [[Karl.Explain]]
<<else>>
    Huh?
<<endif>>
===

title: Karl.Explain
tags: 
---
So you're new here, right? Let me show you around town.
We have a tavern, a tree and this road we are standing on this very second, buddy.
===

title: Karl.ChildOfLadyKatherine
tags: 
---
<<displaypromptmenu Managers OriAAA>>
Wait, are you the child of Lady Katherine? Yes or No?
<<set $katherinemother to react("general", "katherineMother")>>
<<if $katherinemother is true>>
    Woah, LADY KATHERINE is your MOTHER? Please forgive my casual tone.
    I had heard, her child was coming back home. She probably will be very happy.
    I'm sure she is already awaiting you.
<<else>>
    Oh, nevermind, then.
<<endif>>
===

title: Karl.Idle
tags: 
---
<<set $origin to getinfo("placeOfOrigin")>>
<<if getinfo("katherineMother") eq true>>
    Wow, I really can't believe, that you're Lady Katherine's child...
<<elseif getinfo("local") eq true>>
    It's so weird that I cant remember you at all...
<<else>>
    If you have any questions, feel free to ask me! I bet {$origin} is very different to Mayfair.
<<endif>>
===